title: Maybelline New York Lash Sensational Sky High Washable Mascara Makeup, Volumizing, Lengthening, Defining, Curling, Multiplying, Buildable Formula, Blackest Black, 1 Count
description: Sky high lash impact from Every angle! Lash Sensational Sky High mascara delivers full volume and limitless length. Exclusive flex tower mascara brush bends to volumize and extend every single lash from root to tip. Washable mascara formula infused with Bamboo Extract and fibers for long, full lashes that never gets weighed down. Available in very Black and Blackest Black. Allergy tested. Ophthalmologist tested. Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Removes easily.
